item.title: CVE-2022-36928|2024-08-03T10:21:32.309Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20for%20android
item.description: Zoom for Android clients before version 5.13.0 contain a path traversal vulnerability. A third party app could exploit this vulnerability to read and write to the Zoom application data directory.
